---
title: Core - Message center
currentUrl: message-center
---
extends layouts/layout

block content
  .page.pt-5.px-4.pt-sm-6.px-sm-5.pt-xl-7.px-xl-7
    .page-head
      .h3.mb-4.mb-xl-5 Message center
    .page-body.pb-4.pb-xl-6
      .message-block.card.d-flex.flex-row.p-2.p-lg-3
        .message-users.d-flex.flex-column.overflow-hidden.me-0.me-lg-3
          .message-tabs.js-animate-tabs.rounded-pill.p-1.m-3.mb-5
            .tabs.nav.position-relative
              button.tab.d-flex.justify-content-center.p-1.w-50.active(data-bs-toggle="tab")
                +i('profile-circled-fill')
                .text-semibold-1.ms-2 Customers
              button.tab.d-flex.justify-content-center.p-1.w-50(data-bs-toggle="tab")
                +i('zap')
                .text-semibold-1.ms-2 Everyone
              .bg-tab-active.rounded-pill
          +messages_list(demo_messages, false)
          .mt-auto.p-3
            .search-input.input-group.w-100
              button.input-group-text.transparent
                +i('search')
              input.form-control.input-action.rounded-2(type="text" placeholder="Search nessage")
        .message-chat.border.overflow-hidden.rounded-2.w-100
          .message-chat-header.p-4.p-lg-5
            .d-flex.align-items-center
              .title.mb-0.mb-lg-1 Orval Casper
              +action_item.ms-auto
                button.action-item
                  +i('check')
                  | Mark as read
                button.action-item
                  +i('trash')
                  | Delete message
              .message-close.btn-rounded.ms-3.d-block.d-lg-none
                +i('close')
            .message-chat-info.d-none.d-lg-block
              .d-inline-block.pe-3
                span.fs-10.text-shades-2.pe-1 Customer since:
                span.caption-2.text-reset Sep 2021
              .d-inline-block.px-3
                span.fs-10.text-shades-2.pe-1 Purchased:
                span.caption-2.text-reset 21 items
              .d-inline-block.ps-3
                span.fs-10.text-shades-2.pe-1 Lifetime:
                span.caption-2.text-reset $1,235.00
          .mt-4.mt-mb-5.text-center
            .btn-stroke.btn-small Load conversation
          .message-wrapper.d-flex.justify-content-between.flex-column
            .message-chat-body.p-4.p-lg-5
              .d-flex.align-items-start.mb-6
                .message-userpic.flex-shrink-0
                  img.rounded-circle.w-100(src="img/content/user-2.jpg", alt="Orval Casper")
                .ms-4
                  .d-flex.align-items-center
                    .text-semibold-1.text-shades-2.me-3 Orval Casper
                    .caption.text-shades-1 11:59AM
                  .mt-1
                    | When do you release the coded for the Fleet - Travel kit? <a href="https://ui8.net/" target="_blank">https://ui8.net/product-link</a>
              .d-flex.align-items-start.mb-6
                .message-userpic.flex-shrink-0
                  img.rounded-circle.w-100(src="img/content/user-1.jpg", alt="Britney Beer")
                .ms-4
                  .d-flex.align-items-center
                    .text-semibold-1.text-shades-2.me-3 Britney Beer
                    .caption.text-shades-1 11:59AM
                  .mt-1
                    | Hi @orval, thanks for contacting. <br>
                    | Yes, Iâ€™m working on it. It would be released next 2 weeks. You could check the progress here: <a href="https://ui8.net/" target="_blank">https://ui8.net/progress</a> <br><br>
                    | Thanks for your patience and understanding. ðŸ™Œ <br>
                    | Regards, <br><br>
                    | Br

            .message-chat-send.d-flex.align-items-center.p-4.p-lg-5
              .d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center.position-relative.me-5
                input(type="file")
                +i('file-add')
              +smileys
              .input-group.ms-5
                input.form-control.input-action.rounded-2(type="text" placeholder="Message")
                .input-group-text
                  button.btn.btn-small Send



